          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Pathetic school! I wanted my son to go to a school that allowed him to learn and grow up in a toxic free space. My 8 year old son was bullied for months and one day he was beaten up came home with torn clothes, yet the authorities paid no heed. I withdrew him without admission anywhere else as Shikshantar school declined taking any responsibility about things happening on their campus and during school hours.\nOther incidents of bullying of younger children by older students keep happening but the school turns a blind eye.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
