          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "An educational institution with a difference. The campus and grounds are well planned and spread out so that every class and room gets ample air and sunlight 365 days a year. After my own school in Darjeeling this is possibly one of the few schools within a city that has thought about the welfare and wholesome development of a student than concentrating on bookish knowledge only and giving ample space to do so. It is great to see so much being focused on a personality development of our future than just churning out individuals without the guts to face the challenges of life. Love the thoughts that have been implemented behind such a niche in the education system.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
